<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.2618153>
    dc:description "FIGURES 13–21. Trichromothrips moundi sp.n.(13) Head and pronotum. (14) Male sternites IV–VII. (15) Male tergites VIII– X. (16) Tergites II–III of female. (17) Mesonotum and metanotum. (18) Abdominal tergites VIII of female. (19) Female sternites VI–VII. (20) Antennae. (21) Fore wing." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/2618153/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.2618159>
    dc:description "FIGURES 40–50. Trichromothrips genus-group species. (40) T. albus head and pronotum. (41) T. indicus male abdominal sternites III–VII. (42) T. elegans male abdominal tergites VIII–X. (43) Laplothrips bicolor fore wing. (44) T. falcus fore wing. (45) T. trifasciatus fore wing. (46) T. indicus fore wing. (47) Trachynotothrips striatus antennae. (48) T. falcus antennae. (49) T. trifasciatus antennae. (50) O. bhattii abdominal tergite IV." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/2618159/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.2618155>
    dc:description "FIGURES 22–30. Trichromothrips species. T. guizhouensis sp.n. 22–26: (22) Head and pronotum. (23) Abdominal tergites III–X. (24) Mesonotum and metanotum. (25) Fore wing. (26) Antennae. T. antidesmae sp.n. 27–30: (27) Head and pronotum. (28) Male abdominal tergites IX–X. (29) Fore wing. (30) Antennae." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/2618155/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.2618157>
    dc:description "FIGURES 31–39. Head and pronotum of Trichromothrips genus-group species. (31) Laplothrips bicolor. (32) Yoshinothrips pasekamui. (33) Octothrips bhatti. (34) Trachynotothrips striatus. (35) Trichromothrips falcus. (36) T. elegans. (37) T. crispator. (38) T. trifasciatus. (39) T. indicus." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/2618157/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.2618151>
    dc:description "FIGURES 1–12. Trichromothrips genus-group species. Trichromothrips species 1–11: (1) T. moundi female. (2) T. moundi male. (3) T. albus. female (4) T. guizhouensis sp.n. female (5) T. indicus female. (6) T. elegans female. (7) T. elegans male. (8) T. trifasciatus female. (9) T. crispator female. (10) T. antidesmae sp.n. female. (11) T. assamensis female. (12) Trachynotothrips striatus female." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/2618151/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

